2009-06-12 Victor M. Hernandez <victor.hr@gmail.com> 
    * Fork of GtkSheet widget in gtkextra    
	* gtksheetwidget.c: Fixed memory leak in gtk_sheet_range_set_font
	* gtksheetwidget.c: Allocate colors in gtk_sheet_range_set_foreground, 
          gtk_sheet_range_set_background, gtk_sheet_set_grid, 
          gtk_sheet_set_background
    * gtksheetwidget.c: Add properties (very useful for bindings):
        autoresize, autoscroll, clip_text, grid_visible, justify_entry, locked,
        state, columns_resizable, column_titles_visible, rows_resizable,
        row_titles_visible, title, active_cell, selected_range, n_rows, 
        n_columns, selection_mode.
    * gtksheetwidget.c: Fix anonymous enums for GtkSheetBorderFlags and 
        GtkSheetState.
    * gtksheetwidget.c: gtk types for GtkSheetCellBorder and GtkSheetCellAttr
        structures
    * Clean deprecated glib/gtk+ function calls
    * testgtksheet.c: refactored the gtksheet test, fixing a segfault

    
    


